---
import MainGridLayout from "../layouts/MainGridLayout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<MainGridLayout title="关于我">
    <div
        class="flex w-full rounded-[var(--radius-large)] overflow-hidden relative min-h-[70vh]"
    >
        <div
            class="card-base z-10 px-6 py-16 sm:px-16 relative w-full bg-white/70 dark:bg-zinc-900/70 backdrop-blur-3xl"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-10 bg-black/[0.03] dark:bg-white/[0.03] flex items-center px-6 gap-2 border-b border-black/5 dark:border-white/5"
            >
                <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400/50"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-amber-400/50"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/50"></div>
                </div>
                <span
                    class="ml-4 text-[10px] font-mono opacity-30 tracking-widest uppercase"
                    >AboutMe.tsx</span
                >
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center mb-28 mt-10">
                <div class="relative group">
                    <div
                        class="absolute -inset-8 bg-grid-[var(--primary)]/[0.05] [mask-image:radial-gradient(white,transparent)] pointer-events-none"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <img
                        src="https://github.com/ISHAOHAO.png"
                        class="relative w-44 h-44 rounded-[2.5rem] border-2 border-[var(--primary)]/20 shadow-2xl object-cover transition-all duration-700 group-hover:rounded-[1rem]"
                        alt="Avatar"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-black/5 dark:border-white/10 flex items-center gap-2"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-bold opacity-80 uppercase tracking-tighter"
                            >CS Freshman</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center mt-12">
                    <h1
                        class="text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-4 font-mono"
                    >
                        <span class="text-[var(--primary)] opacity-50"
                            >&lt;</span
                        >ISHAOHAO<span class="text-[var(--primary)] opacity-50">
                            /&gt;</span
                        >
                    </h1>
                    <p
                        class="text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-sm uppercase"
                    >
                        从 0 到 1 的技术探险者
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-32">
                <section class="reveal-slide">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                        <div
                            class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-zinc-200 dark:to-zinc-800"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <h2
                            class="text-xs font-black text-[var(--primary)] uppercase tracking-[0.5em]"
                        >
                            Console.log("WhoAmI")
                        </h2>
                        <div
                            class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-zinc-200 dark:to-zinc-800"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="text-lg leading-loose text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 font-medium text-center"
                    >
                        一名大一在读的计算机系学生。目前正在努力驯服 <span
                            class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white font-bold"
                            >Vue/JavaScript</span
                        >、深入探索 <span
                            class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white font-bold"
                            >前端美学</span
                        >。
                        对我来说，编程不仅是完成作业的工具，它是构建想象空间的魔法。
                        <div
                            class="mt-8 py-6 px-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900/5 dark:bg-white/5 border-dashed border-2 border-zinc-900/10 dark:border-white/10 text-base italic opacity-80"
                        >
                            “比起成为大神，我更享受在这个数字世界里横冲直撞的乐趣。”
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="reveal-slide">
                    <h2
                        class="text-xs font-black text-[var(--primary)] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-center mb-12"
                    >
                        正在学习的项目
                    </h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        {
                            [
                                {
                                    title: "编程语言",
                                    list: "HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Python",
                                    color: "bg-blue-500",
                                },
                                {
                                    title: "开发工具",
                                    list: "VS Code, Git, GitHub, PyCharm, IntelliJ IDEA",
                                    color: "bg-emerald-500",
                                },
                                {
                                    title: "当前研究",
                                    list: "数据结构, 现代网页设计",
                                    color: "bg-purple-500",
                                },
                                {
                                    title: "生活兴趣",
                                    list: "数码硬件, 摄影, 旅行",
                                    color: "bg-amber-500",
                                },
                            ].map((item) => (
                                <div class="group p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-white/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500">
                                    <div
                                        class={`w-2 h-12 ${item.color} rounded-full mb-6`}
                                    />
                                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2">
                                        {item.title}
                                    </h3>
                                    <p class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
                                        {item.list}
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            ))
                        }
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="reveal-slide pb-20">
                    <div
                        class="relative p-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-[var(--primary)] to-purple-500 rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 px-8 py-14 rounded-[2.9rem] flex flex-col items-center"
                        >
                            <h2
                                class="text-4xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-6 italic tracking-tighter"
                            >
                                Build with me.
                            </h2>
                            <p
                                class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 text-center mb-10 max-w-sm"
                            >
                                既然路过，不如留个联系方式？无论是技术交流还是吐槽高数，我都随时在线。
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
                                <a
                                    href="mailto:me@ishaohao.cn"
                                    class="px-10 py-4 bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-zinc-100 text-white dark:text-black font-bold rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform active:scale-95"
                                >
                                    发送邮件
                                </a>
                                <a
                                    href="https://github.com/ISHAOHAO"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    class="p-4 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-[var(--primary)] hover:text-white transition-all"
                                >
                                    <Icon
                                        name="fa6-brands:github"
                                        class="w-6 h-6"
                                    />
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainGridLayout>

<style is:global>
    /* 极致的背景网格 */
    .bg-grid-primary {
        background-image: radial-gradient(var(--primary) 1px, transparent 0);
        background-size: 30px 30px;
    }

    /* 优雅的入场动画 */
    .reveal-slide {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
        animation: revealIn 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    }

    @keyframes revealIn {
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    section:nth-child(1) {
        animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }
    section:nth-child(2) {
        animation-delay: 0.4s;
    }
    section:nth-child(3) {
        animation-delay: 0.6s;
    }
</style>
